{"tid":2433082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【親屬看不見的他們　依然精神抖擻】","createTime":"2021-03-04T17:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T10:43:42.000Z","uid":126919,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bff4ce97bfe9268feee41604c8d569734ecc65d5","tid":2433082,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"【親屬看不見的他們　依然精神抖擻】<br />\n<br />\n四天法庭程序完結，47名被指「串謀顛覆國家政權」的被告，結果全再遭羈押。由於被告所在的法庭只容許代表律師進入，親屬也不能在正庭聽審，所以各被告家屬，其實都無法見到被告一眼。<br />\n<br />\n被告之二的鄒家成和岑敖暉坐懲教車回到荔枝角收押所時下車，二人一同舉起手指公，期間眾懲教人員喝止。同車的還有譚文豪、陣志全、梁晃維、林卓廷、朱凱廸、岑子杰等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dAweJcE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdAweJcE.jpg&h=5c8e4844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3953211754764415/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3953211754764415%2F&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9dc6931b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3953211754764415/</a>"},{"pid":"caa16d8e101758532c9ebe471d0c81b1065309ce","tid":2433082,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287cb57eef774ede331af5acb62bab7161b270a1","tid":2433082,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c7ec9f885fad81bb5557e274d152f